text: Delaney Schnell (born December 21, 1998) is an American diver.Team USA profile Schnell is a student at the University of Arizona, where she also competes in diving. 2018-19 Women's Swimming and Diving Roster She participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning a bronze medal in women's 10 metre platform competition.10 metre platform results ==References== ==External links== *Delaney Schnell profile at TeamUSA.org *Delaney Schnell profile at Arizona Wildcats * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:American female divers Category:Sportspeople from Tucson, Arizona Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in diving Category:Arizona Wildcats women's divers Category:Pan American Games medalists in diving Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for the United States Category:Divers at the 2019 Pan American Games
